Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,song,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.77,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:13.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There you go, making that \Ndepressing face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.45,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:17.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:21.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She'll wake up soon just \Nlike Kaname and I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:24.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:29.05,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's been one week since\NManaka-san came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:31.37,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone believed somewhere \Nin their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:30.43,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:34.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What the hell is with \NEnglish being first period?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:35.32,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That she'd be the same \Nas Hikari or Kaname-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:37.64,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That she'd wake up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:39.10,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:44.41,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san still showed \Nno signs of waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.70,Episode-Title - Copy,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty: \N Sleeping Beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:21.07,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,That ends our lesson for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.57,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Those who finish cleaning \Nfirst can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:26.00,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's a lot of homework, \Nbut don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:26.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.09,Main,girl bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:29.07,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the bathroom \Ncleaning over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:29.07,Main,boy bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day I'm \Ngonna catch that Uroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:36.36,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama may know a \Nway to wake Manaka up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:39.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, considering he's the one \Nwho made everyone hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:43.97,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:46.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:51.15,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that Hikari would be \Nmore panicked about Manaka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.96,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,but he seems pretty positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.82,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Is Manaka-san at your house \Nby herself during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:01.11,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's been getting days off \Nfrom Saya Mart to take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.82,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:09.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is he hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.51,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,The water temperature's getting lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.19,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:23.05,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a lot lower since the \Nday we found Manaka in Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:27.60,Flashback,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(314,1)}Could it be that the Sea God is angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.89,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,223)}About us taking Manaka back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All we have to do is \Ncome up to the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,once in a while and warm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.16,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.63,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't rested since \Nyou came back up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.71,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Chisaki's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.92,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd be late \Nbecause of her internship...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.73,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we just missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.36,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.82,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go take a look again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.82,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:35.37,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to go to Shishio \Nwith the others, Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to leave Shishio
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.89,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,to Hikari and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:47.78,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that since \Nwe're all the same age now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:51.35,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be nice if we could \Ndo more things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:56.13,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,And it'd be even nicer if we \Ncould get closer to their circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.86,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.69,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about Manaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.06,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,How about stimulating her five senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.46,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Like stimulating her ears\Nby playing her a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.24,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:11.48,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:15.31,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan said she met \Nhim in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.50,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a look at the \Noutskirts of the village, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.07,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:35.09,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,The song's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:38.27,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of the \Nday of the Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.13,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.21,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Every day at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.10,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka heard this song, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might have come \Nup with a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.70,Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.21,Local Mascot Character,board,0000,0000,0000,,Local Mascot Character Name Ideas: \NOshiosshii\NSea Slug-kun\NNarunamimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.21,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.42,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If we let her listen to \Nthings from the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,something will like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:04.67,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Scenes from that day will \Ncome up in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:08.64,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We think that might just wake Manaka up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:12.81,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,But people have been coming and \Ngoing quite a bit since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:16.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Gather whomever you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So Itaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.17,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,We beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.83,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:24.61,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:27.93,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go contact some people, \Nso could you wait a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.42,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.81,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:46.42,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.30,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.61,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.01,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The bath's ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.39,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.13,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.61,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:11.48,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really are complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:19.25,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.27,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki-chan and Kaname \Nare with him, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.27,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.48,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I was a little worried about \Nthose three at first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.76,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki-chan's been coming \Nby a lot more often lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.56,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Now if only Manaka-chan would wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:35.26,Manaka Wake Up,picture,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka Wake Up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.26,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.29,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, apparently \NHikari and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:41.02,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,asked the fishery cooperative \Nto record the song for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.02,notebook,,0000,0000,0000,,-Sounds to stimulate her ears...?\N-... from the sea.\N-Nostalgic music: like from the Ofunehiki
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.03,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He's gathering people from \Nthe Ofunehiki five years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:48.43,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,in the hope that it might\Nwake Manaka-chan up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:52.76,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I think Itaru-san was pretty happy \Nbecause he called me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:56.03,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he wasn't the one who \Nthought of it, he's super excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.55,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't catch Uroko today either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.56,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.09,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,We got a lot of homework today, \Nso let's do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:29.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Everyone \Nwas complaining about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:33.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There really isn't that much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll take some \Ntime off from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.17,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That'll give me a lot more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll be able to do a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.08,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"No"? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:44.66,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,we're still required to go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you being all serious for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:50.68,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And Mom will be really worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari's not my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.03,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.27,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Taking time off from school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't ever wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.06,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to go to school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.02,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:08.86,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.62,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:17.13,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I wanted to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.81,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:31.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I was fine just the way I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.96,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:42.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,the sea and the surface kept freezing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.80,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.37,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.67,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He left for the sea a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.37,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd go to school \Nstraight from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:07.92,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ketchup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.38,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akira! What do you \Nthink you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:15.01,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the Warring States \Nera finally came to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.01,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, the 260 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:21.38,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,People who push their own feelings \Nonto others are awful, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:21.39,Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Library
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.62,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:26.78,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the \Nprotagonist in this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:30.41,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to read books \Nthat don't concern Manaka-san today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:34.15,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,But we've been sitting \Nhere for three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.77,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Even my concentration is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.74,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,or rather, what are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.50,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's an actual relevant book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.87,Learning About Sleep,book,0000,0000,0000,,Learning About Sleep \N{\fs16}The True State of Hypnosis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.64,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a little off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:47.36,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know where we'll find \Na clue about her waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.19,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you actually thinking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.57,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.17,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.16,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.92,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.84,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't princes do that often?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.37,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss the sleeping princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.26,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I think someone should try that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.27,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,on the sleeping Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.77,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wh— a-a kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.81,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.14,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I think that strong feelings for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:16.66,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,have the power to change\N something drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Strong feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.99,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who have that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.76,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Like Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:29.04,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it wouldn't be good to kiss her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.16,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,if there's no solid \Nproof that it'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.52,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do you have a better idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:37.08,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Not... right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.36,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Then why does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.83,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:44.80,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like you don't really \Nwant Manaka-san to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.97,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who just said we don't \Nknow where we might find a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.89,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being pretty serious about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:58.61,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really not want \NManaka-san to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.89,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.67,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go look \Nfor Uroko-sama again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.50,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Hoi, hoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:23.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.34,The Ofunehiki Song,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Ofunehiki Song
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.34,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Hoi, hoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.00,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I want Manaka-san to wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.06,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I should have been \Nthinking this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.25,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Was I the only one that \Nwas somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:48.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:52.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,When did you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.46,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.08,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.48,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.92,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.48,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have him stay home \Nfrom school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.08,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You should get to bed, too, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.69,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be no good if everyone keels over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.71,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.83,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.34,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it almost time for \Nyou to leave for school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.60,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Miu has a fever, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.43,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.89,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,let's just say that she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.81,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.45,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.73,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.65,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Miuna and Hikari have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.50,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them are absent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.76,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:07.95,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.41,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.51,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,The sea's cold, and you've been\Ngoing in with Hikari, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.10,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.25,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.04,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.29,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,That Hikari, trying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.75,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Miuna and I and \Neveryone else are here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.21,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.52,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:28.84,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to take notes \Nfor three people today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.37,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,For three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:35.41,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna's been taking notes for \NManaka-san for when she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.60,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.63,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help with taking notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:41.61,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.14,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.61,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.49,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's sleeping pretty well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.24,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to take \NAkira and go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.95,Main,mutter,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.08,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.26,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And you told Hikari not to rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:34.77,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really not want \NManaka-san to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.53,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.47,Italics,hikari tape,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Hey, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.53,Italics,akira tape,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.89,Italics,hikari tape,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.97,Italics,akira tape,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:11.40,The Ofunehiki Song,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Ofunehiki Song
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:08.42,Italics,hikari tape,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go find Uroko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.40,Italics,hikari tape,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the one who wakes her up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.03,Italics,hikari tape,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:16.95,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari is always so straight \Nand narrow and bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.70,The Ofunehiki Song,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Ofunehiki Song
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.70,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.90,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,his feelings for Manaka-san \Nmake him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:26.54,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And yet I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:28.93,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.67,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been reported that just like in \Nmountain climbing and free diving,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.87,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,when you put yourself into \Ndangerous situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.93,Water,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Water
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.71,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,there's a rarely seen phenomenon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.51,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,that in order to stay alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:44.19,Main,prof overlap,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}To solve why Mukaido-san is still \Nsleeping and why Shiodome-san has Ena...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.36,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,your dormant survival instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:44.18,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,bring changes upon your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:48.21,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that your \NEna is also a result
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:53.70,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,of your dormant sea-person powers\Nawakening because you were pushed to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.46,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The professor would like \Nto talk to you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.09,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a day that works best for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.09,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:04.45,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,When do you think we can see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.18,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:08.46,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.44,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come out right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:19.97,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.44,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You had quite a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:25.72,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,but it's gone down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.05,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you thank Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.36,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,She's been watching \Nover you up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What about Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:34.19,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,There haven't been any changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.81,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, I understand \Nhow you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.68,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,you should rely on those \Naround you a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're lecturing a sick person?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:46.06,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one who \Ncares about Manaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.33,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.56,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:59.11,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname-kun and Sayu-chan \Nbrought them by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:01.71,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys won't be \Nbehind in your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.82,Corn Porridge,can,0000,0000,0000,,Corn Soup
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.82,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.79,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.82,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.82,Tangerine Juice,can,0000,0000,0000,,Tangerine Juice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:20.89,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.49,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:28.16,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I really am hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.67,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.01,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:34.53,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The guys from Shishio are \Noverflowing with emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.26,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been a \Nlittle envious of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:42.08,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.77,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably not a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.77,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not like \NHikari and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:52.17,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Before when Hikari saw my Ena,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.52,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,he said I was just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But... I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.94,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Manaka-san losing her Ena
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.41,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,and why did I gain Ena?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:10.23,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one with different \Nfeelings toward Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:13.42,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I said something weird to \NHikari and upset him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.50,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't ever wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.42,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of the worst thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:25.14,Flashback-Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really not want \NManaka-san to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.30,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.86,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,seriously thought it'd be better
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.58,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,if they didn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.70,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:45.07,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like Chisaki \Nwould disappear from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.16,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,and I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.76,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:52.68,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,once they woke up, I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.99,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,"Happy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.04,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:59.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:04.59,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You were scared but happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:06.23,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.40,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.94,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,if I'll be able to be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:15.69,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for you because \Nthey're both precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:19.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Both Hikari and Mukaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:24.65,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:28.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to say I'm glad
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.08,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:42.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently they've taken notes \Nfor you while you were out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:45.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna and the others took them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.07,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to wake up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:55.17,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.24,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,She will. No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.65,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:04.72,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,There's something Sayu was telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:05.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:06.49,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:10.65,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Strong feelings for someone have the \Nability to change something drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty sure that you have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:15.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,powers like that, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.33,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:21.87,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:22.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:23.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:29.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:30.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.02,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.32,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.14,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that you \Nshould kiss Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! Either way, why would I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.91,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's needed for her to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:41.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And why would that need a k-kiss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.97,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:47.64,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to \Nget that mad at girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's because she—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:52.98,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:33.24,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,How was she? How was Mukaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:34.83,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,She was so energetic, it startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:36.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:37.49,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka is Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:38.81,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're back...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.73,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,The Four from Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.77,Episode-Title - Copy,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty-One: \N The Messenger from the Bottom of the Sea
